Class MockDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.MockDataManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataManagerAPI
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class MockDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataManagerAPI
    [TESTING ONLY - Singleton Model Class] A singleton instance of the DataManagerAPI for the frontend objects to interact with while the real data manager is being created and tested. Returns hard coded objects for each method defined in the interface
    See Also:
    DataManagerAPI, HabitEvent, Created by fraserbulbuc on 2017-11-07.
